{"tid":246950,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個身邊最痴線既朋友","createTime":"2017-05-17T11:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T03:49:57.000Z","uid":28619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a11031099e87b196806103214fb04fec4048972a","tid":246950,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"中4個陣識個frd，佢話好鍾意睇回魂夜，每日都會重睇<br />\n初頭以為佢假膠，後來一齊食lunch 先知佢真係日日開住電話睇送飯，好撚癲"},{"pid":"0f8fa6842fa807247fe26504f4ad6cbee3d64480","tid":246950,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"有特異功能<br />\n從來唔出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71cf4bb7691822336712d14c8e2a2b574aaa4437","tid":246950,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:30:23.000Z","msg":"只要同我哋獨處就會做好多痴線嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大聲鳩叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個就係我<br />\n仲有個<br />\n我教佢咩叫1Q，教佢講幾錢Q<br />\n而家日日講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114c2cd1446429722250ee13e1b356a57c91c974","tid":246950,"uid":106177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:52:35.000Z","msg":"我中學有個friend 佢可以用自己條j 好似啪手指咁 啪啲聲"},{"pid":"a9e052f02b92cd290664a3ab5d081cc72426ab72","tid":246950,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我中學有個friend 佢可以用自己條j 好似啪手指咁 啪啲聲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4faa96fe84231fc41ed799280f6fc5f3863478","tid":246950,"uid":108756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"每次見到有狗行過都會同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知隻狗有咩藥用功效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9185b9d01c343a9e0bed67d46ea25baed6fb13","tid":246950,"uid":33809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"有個朋友會週街扮狗吠，有次吠到俾警犬逗。<br />\n<br />\n我諗果兩個警犬以為我朋友串緊佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f3c6117b74ecf0a36b60c81ea327bb007ecd2f","tid":246950,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:39:32.000Z","msg":"行行下街可以係過馬路個陣跳舞仲要係bigbang太陽個啲舞<br />\n成日講啲關於gay佬既問題<br />\n成日無端端搭膊頭用手指畫圈咁畫個肩膊位<br />\n上面係我會做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係對同一個朋友做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就來逼到佢癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1adfa8e21d092f4f667557a15d843b188e4af26","tid":246950,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個朋友會週街扮狗吠，有次吠到俾警犬逗。<br />\n<br />\n我諗果兩個警犬以為我朋友串緊佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前試過有個朋友同我講話<br />\n嗱如果行街撞到警察佢有望住你呢<br />\n你就堅定啲望返佢望實佢<br />\n好啦之後有一次同另一個朋友（我地三個互相認識）行街<br />\n咁啱見到警察係前面<br />\n有一個望住我<br />\n我用朋友講個招<br />\n望實個警察<br />\n一秒 兩秒<br />\n警察同我講先生唔該睇睇身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一個警察諗住一路行架啦都停低埋查我同個朋友<br />\n我另一個朋友都唔知咩事俾人查<br />\n我同佢講返係另一個朋友咁樣講過<br />\n佢屌到我同朋友到今時今日都仲屌緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經過左四五年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd83974c79fac790153558f4282363b262db4f1","tid":246950,"uid":52903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:30:14.000Z","msg":"好驚見到有人話緊我"},{"pid":"126b9acec89204af3601c5ca622708d2e2a96522","tid":246950,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我中學有個friend 佢可以用自己條j 好似啪手指咁 啪啲聲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條j有節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067f561b99958165b41be58918ef800b23f93721","tid":246950,"uid":106177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T23:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我中學有個friend 佢可以用自己條j 好似啪手指咁 啪啲聲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條j有節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢仲要上緊堂啪比我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522b0b78dfa8f392925a0709933384310b87a45b","tid":246950,"uid":64193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T23:53:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我中學有個friend 佢可以用自己條j 好似啪手指咁 啪啲聲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條j有節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢仲要上緊堂啪比我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係啪啪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a0448e6fbc6b231be7c7c2d4b34713aae77d0f","tid":246950,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T23:55:43.000Z","msg":"細個成個講去叫雞<br />\n點知大個左真係去叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e082a37b6ea699e32539317d79753f072d0b6c5f","tid":246950,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個成個講去叫雞<br />\n點知大個左真係去叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d526a78f7cf370c8be64b2f44b4a5d171008712","tid":